name: Material Design Icons
description:
Instant easy access to the entire Material Design Icons library.


27,000 new icons, available in PNG and SVG.


Search icons by name or scroll through the entire list. Filter by category, change style and size, and choose between different styles: filled, outlined, rounded, etc.


What's inside

  • Free icons by Google. You can find them in the "Google" section.
  • Free icons by Icons8. We offer an extensive free tier. All we ask is for you to add a link back to Icons8.com, crediting us in the final work. If you don't want to add a link, consider buying a license. Additionally, you'll get access to all formats and sizes.


Original creator: Grappex.com
